milestones.description: Geoff Boycott has scored 6 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for ENG breaking Fletcher's record
Alvin Kallicharran has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (24) for WI, going past Clive Lloyd
Andy Roberts has become the highest wicket-taker in ODIs with 43 wickets, going past Chris Old's 41
Viv Richards has scored 9 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Ian Chappell's record
